headline: "A Lot of Liquidity in the Bond Market": Citigroup's Zogheb

headline: Citigroup to face lawsuit over alleged involvement in Oceanografia’s fraud
summary: The 11th US Circuit Court of Appeals in Miami has ruled that the previously dismissed case holds merit and Citigroup may have substantially aided the fraudulent activities.
